019-08-05T18:33:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:35:19.000Z","msg":"我應該係ies拉高咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我記得係頭三 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:36:20.000Z","msg":"咁坦白講仲難，除非搵啱補習"},{"pid":"d3eae5cc01fce760d49d489c41ba1ea7ffa6d7a8","tid":1414603,"uid":208499,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:21:21.000Z","msg":"Retake過ls<br />\n補左好多習<br />\n一樣 第一次考又係裸考 同拎4<br />\n但補習確實有用 會明ls點玩<br />\n但最後...都係4左<br />\n都係睇彩數多<br />\n我就係衰控制唔到時間 第一次考嗰陣 會冇野寫到剩好多時間<br />\n第二次考就寫到...第三題(a)同(b)吉哂 仲有條2(a)....<br />\n自己問題<br />\n但如果想升既話 真係建議補習<br />\n希望你最後成功升分"},{"pid":"264ced7c43373b3d02f44344f28f1c6b2e1067ba","tid":1414603,"uid":299445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f830b328e96ba2257df6bbb7fcd6b8411a76bfd","tid":1414603,"uid":184509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3eae5cc01fce760d49d489c41ba1ea7ffa6d7a8","tid":1414603,"uid":208499,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:21:21.000Z","msg":"Retake過ls<br />\n補左好多習<br />\n一樣 第一次考又係裸考 同拎4<br />\n但補習確實有用 會明ls點玩<br />\n但最後...都係4左<br />\n都係睇彩數多<br />\n我就係衰控制唔到時間 第一次考嗰陣 會冇野寫到剩好多時間<br />\n第二次考就寫到...第三題(a)同(b)吉哂 仲有條2(a)....<br />\n自己問題<br />\n但如果想升既話 真係建議補習<br />\n希望你最後成功升分"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:54:40.000Z","msg":"但最後...都係4左<br />\n咁咪姐係補黎哂9氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae83a177eda033392f080ff8ff2a059fb259a14","tid":1414603,"uid":224829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:57:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f40f5d227f56706ec036ab1d338a061301f4e32","tid":1414603,"uid":143307,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1534358021e220417